["Haizhu Square Station (Chinese: \u6d77\u73e0\u5e7f\u573a\u7ad9 ) is an interchange station of Line 2 and Line 6 of the Guangzhou Metro. It started operations on 29 December 2002. It is situated underneath Guangzhou Qiyi Road,[1] Yide Road[2] and Taikang Road[3] in Yuexiu District. It is near Haizhu Square, Guangzhou Hotel (\u5e7f\u5dde\u9152\u5e97 ) and Hotel Canton Landmark (\u534e\u590f\u5927\u9152\u5e97 ).[4][5]","Both the line 2 and line 6 stations have underground island platforms.","The station has 7 exits, lettered A, B (B1 to B3) and D to F."]